# Design System - shadcn/ui

## Design System Reference

**Use the [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com) design system as the foundation for all UI components and styling.**

### Installation & Reference

- **Installation Docs**: 
  - Main installation: [https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation)
  - Next.js specific: [https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/next](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/next)
  - React Router: [https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/react-router](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/react-router)
