Reference the [shadcn/ui documentation](https://ui.shadcn.com) for the full component library.

### Implementation Pattern

When implementing shadcn/ui components:
1. Review the component documentation on shadcn/ui
2. Adapt the component code to work within browser extension CSP constraints
3. Ensure styles are self-contained (no external dependencies)
4. Maintain consistency with shadcn/ui design patterns
